data.description: Assumable 5.5% FHA loan sets this serene Norman home apart. Recent renovations prior to 2023 include wood-look tile, a modern kitchen with white quartz countertops, herringbone backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Dishwasher replaced in 2023. Master ensuite boasts double vanities, walk-in closet, and a wet room with double shower heads and a large tub. The property spans just over 2 acres, includes a 40x60 shop with a fully insulated 20x15 room, and a cattle gate on the driveway. Roof replaced in 2021. Prioritize a viewing to appreciate this unique offering.
